election, specialization and genome size.</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Molecular ecology</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/person/dabc2fa8e4f99435d8ff3eaf1407da03"><gtr:id>dabc2fa8e4f99435d8ff3eaf1407da03</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Gardiner A</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2008-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:issn>0962-1083</gtr:issn></gtr:publication><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/2D4E8156-C53D-4FF0-8943-33D71720EFE3"><gtr:id>2D4E8156-C53D-4FF0-8943-33D71720EFE3</gtr:id><gtr:title>Introduction. Speciation in plants and animals: pattern and process.</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Philosophical transactions of the Royal Society of London. Series B, Biological sciences</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/person/f2b9d77d065cedd6a178e9f762819463"><gtr:id>f2b9d77d065cedd6a178e9f762819463</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Abbott RJ</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2008-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:issn>0962-8436</gtr:issn></gtr:publication><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/0820570B-D340-4A5A-B821-E4675B3C0AEF"><gtr:id>0820570B-D340-4A5A-B821-E4675B3C0AEF</gtr:id><gtr:title>Genetics of speciation.</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Heredity</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/person/11bc1a2c784bed046257df0be1933919"><gtr:id>11bc1a2c784bed046257df0be1933919</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Butlin RK</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2009-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:issn>0018-067X</gtr:issn></gtr:publication><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/23B97481-E948-426A-ABC6-12B120511018"><gtr:id>23B97481-E948-426A-ABC6-12B120511018</gtr:id><gtr:title>Sites of evolutionary divergence differ between olfactory and gustatory receptors of Drosophila.</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Biology letters</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr: